com.solarsystem

Interface Movable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Asteroid, Comet, DistantStar, Moon, OrbitingSpaceObject, Planet

    public interface Movable
    A simple interface which provides a single move method. Classes who choose to implement this interface can provide custom moving functionality.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void move(SolarSystem system)
      Abstract move method to be implemented by moving space object classes.
